            "x": 110,
            "y": 236,
            "animation": "fade"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "Two-pointer skeleton\n\nThis is the common shape for sorted two-sum: initialize both ends, loop while they have not crossed, then move one side.\n\n- This is the common shape for sorted two-sum: initialize both ends\n- loop while they have not crossed\n- then move one side.",
